---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Início | Catálogo de Páscoa">
  <section style={{
    textAlign: "center",
    flex: "1",
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "column",
    alignItems: "center",
    justifyContent: "center",
    width: "100%",
  }}>
    <h2
      style={{
        color: "#2d1e17",
        fontSize: "clamp(1.5rem, 5vh, 2.8rem)",
        marginBottom: "clamp(0.75rem, 2vh, 1.5rem)",
        marginTop: 0,
      }}
    >
      Bem-vindo à Emily Confeitaria!
    </h2>

    <p
      style={{
        color: "#555",
        fontSize: "clamp(1rem, 2.2vh, 1.3rem)",
        lineHeight: "1.6",
        maxWidth: "560px",
        margin: `0 auto clamp(0.5rem, 1.5vh, 1rem) auto`,
      }}
    >
      Nesta Páscoa, preparamos opções deliciosas e artesanais para você
      presentear quem você ama (ou a si mesmo!).
    </p>

    <p class="destaque-frase">
      Aqui no nosso catálogo, você pode montar o seu ovo de Páscoa
      exatamente do seu jeito!
    </p>

    <a
      href="/pedido"
      class="btn-principal"
    >
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0">
        <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/>
      </svg>
      Montar meu Ovo de Páscoa
    </a>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .destaque-frase {
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2.4vh, 1.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #2d1e17;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
    animation: surgir 0.7s ease-out both;
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .destaque-frase::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: #e2b05b;
    border-radius: 2px;
    animation: linha 0.6s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.9s;
  }

  @keyframes surgir {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(12px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes linha {
    from { width: 0; }
    to { width: 60%; }
  }

  .btn-principal {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: clamp(1rem, 3vh, 2rem);
    padding: clamp(0.8rem, 2vh, 1.1rem) clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    background-color: #2d1e17;
    color: #e2b05b;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vh, 1.25rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(45, 30, 23, 0.25);
    transition: background-color 0.25s, color 0.25s, border-color 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s, transform 0.15s;
  }

  .btn-principal:hover {
    background-color: #e2b05b;
    color: #2d1e17;
    border-color: #2d1e17;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(226, 176, 91, 0.45);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-principal:active {
    transform: translateY(0);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(45, 30, 23, 0.2);
  }
</style>
